    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>ISSUE TYPE: Story</p>

<p>Summary: Improve website usability and modernize design</p>

<p>Description:</p>

<p>Objective<br/>
The website needs to be improved to provide a more user-friendly experience, a modern design, and overall better usability.</p>

<p>Context<br/>
The current version may have usability issues, outdated design elements, and opportunities for improvement in performance, accessibility, and conversion optimization.</p>

<p>Scope of Work</p>

<p>Lucas is responsible for:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Improving user experience (UX).</li>
	<li>Modernizing the visual design (UI).</li>
	<li>Optimizing navigation and site structure.</li>
	<li>Improving loading speed and overall performance.</li>
	<li>Ensuring fully responsive design (mobile and tablet).</li>
	<li>Reviewing basic accessibility standards (contrast, font sizes, labels).</li>
	<li>Improving semantic structure and basic SEO.</li>
	<li>Proposing additional improvements based on current best practices.</li>
</ul>


<p>Acceptance Criteria</p>

<ul>
	<li>The interface has a modern and consistent design.</li>
	<li>Navigation is clear and intuitive.</li>
	<li>The website is fully responsive.</li>
	<li>Performance improves compared to the current version.</li>
	<li>No existing functionality is broken.</li>
	<li>All technical changes are documented.</li>
</ul>


<p>Definition of Done (DoD)</p>

<ul>
	<li>Design approved by the team.</li>
	<li>Code review completed and approved.</li>
	<li>Functional testing completed.</li>
	<li>Deployment to development environment validated.</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
